description.displayText: Jenna was the only person that we trusted to look after our daughter.  A true Care.com success story!  She was dependable right from the beginning.  She cared for our daughter from the age of 3 months to 2 years.  She was always available and on time.  She put our new parent minds at ease right away because she is clearly well-versed with child care, child safety, and child development.  Our daughter was always so happy to see her and could care less that we were leaving!  We love you Jenna!

description.displayText: There are very few people our 10 month old will go to willingly the first time he meets them, and Jenna was one of those people.  We needed someone very last minute, and from the minute she walked in the door I was at ease.  She is a natural.

description.displayText: Jenna was such an amazing asset for us in our time of need, a summer.  The kids took to her wonderfully and I was always impressed with her professionalism and pleasant demeanor.  In addition to what we asked of her relative to the children, she helped around the house without being asked and her attitude was always cheerful, even as she maintained the appropriate level of authority with the children.  She regularly, daily, planned outings to the zoo, museum, pool, etc. as we had requested.  At home I frequently found her entertaining the children outside on the play set or in the sprinkler.  She quickly determined what foods the kids enjoyed and prepared them regularly.  She has my highest recommendation.  I wish she were still here!

description.displayText: Jenna has been working for us as our nanny for the last couple of months, filling in for our nanny that needed a leave of absence.  We have 4 kids ranging from 8 months to 7 yrs and she has managed them all wonderfully well.  We are so glad that we found her and plan to continue using her for babysitting when our previous nanny returns.
